  <p>
    So! As for our audience, we’ve reaffirmed that our messaging should resonate
    with people who are technical. And our best audience is technical and business
    minded. So for now, at least, we’re not going to make efforts to connect with a
    non-technical audience or people who are not in the field.
  </p>
</div>
